text: Karl Bruno Paul Neukirch was a gymnast from Germany. Karl competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on 3 November 1864 and died on 27 June 1941.Karl Neukirch == References == Category:1864 births Category:1941 deaths Category:German gymnasts Category:Olympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Sportspeople from Berlin
